node.text: A little birdie told us there would be a @rjglass x @bigzglass colab at the show 👀😎 Guess he was right!! What a gem from the two masters of glass 🤯💎 This one will be available TOMORROW 8.7.21 🥵❤️ See everyone there!

Just a buffet of GEMS coming at you TOMORROW 8.7.21 for our @bigzglass show 🤩🪐 This one is a sick nasty colab with the one and only @jdz____ 🥵👀 Cannot get over the intensity of this piece there is so much going on at once it’s hard to catch it all 🤯💥 This will be available TOMORROW 8.7.21 😎💪 See everyone there and DM us if you have any questions about the show 🧑‍🚀🚀❤️

node.text: 👀🥵 @hendyglass X @bigzglass this one is very special to us! We had the opportunity to bring these two together for this amazing piece and we couldn’t be more happy with the way it turned out 🤩💎 Those one will be available THIS SATURDAY 8.7.21 🧑‍🚀🚀

Couldn’t be more fire than @bigzglass X @echelonglass 😍🔥 Absolute stunner made with “Stargazer” and some insane sections of @bigzglass space tech 🪐✨ A true honor to have this piece apart of the show THIS SATURDAY 8.7.21 big shoutout to both artists for blessing us 🥵👀 Swipe for the func! 🧑‍🚀🚀

node.text: We had to hit you with a heater right off the bat 😎🔥 Presenting the @rycraftedglass X @bigzglass gill cycler colab 🥵💎 This jaw dropper is stacked with @bigzglass famous space tech matched with a monster cab full of fume work and tons of opals 😍👀 This gem is also signed by both artists and comes in a signed pelican 🤯🤘 We will have her available THIS SATURDAY 8.7.21 for our @bigzglass show 🤩🔥 Hit that DM if you have any questions 🧑‍🚀🚀

node.text: Look what showed up 🤩💥 @bigzglass X @soup_glass SLAYED this tool colab 🤯💎 This is in Royal Jelly with a 20mm opal pillar fitted right in the handle 😍👀 This gem will be available THIS SATURDAY 8.7.21 along with more from these two very talented artists 💪💦 Stay tuned for more peeks 🧑‍🚀🚀

The best things in life come in small wooden boxes 😎🔥 These @seigaiha.glass slurper sets are some of the cleanest out 🥵💥 We will have ten sets dropping tonight in store at 6PM(est) then join us live at 7:10PM(est) on our @planetcaravandrops page for the live showcase and finally make your scoops on the website www.planetcaravansmokeshop.com at 8:10PM(est) 😊💎 See everyone there and hit that DM if you have any questions 🧑‍🚀🚀
